@3001 = ~Turns out this was easily done. I know how to write this now too.~
@3002 = ~I could turn the Cursed Scroll of Weakness into a useful spell scroll. Let me know if you want me to rewrite it.~
@3003 = ~With pleasure.~
@3004 = ~I changed it into a scroll of Horror.~
@3005 = ~I could turn the Cursed Scroll of Ugliness into a useful spell scroll. Let me know if you want me to rewrite it.~
@3006 = ~I changed it into a scroll of Monster Summoning I.~
@3007 = ~I could turn the Cursed Scroll of Summon Monster into a useful spell scroll. Let me know if you want me to rewrite it.~
